teamSubtitle: click bellow to get to know us better!
teamDzoni: My fellow colleague Katrina gave me the task to write something meaningful about myself in 260 characters, so here's my story: I'm a designer. Sometimes I run trails.
teamAlex: An enthusiastic, experienced, and fully qualified designer with passion for UI and UX.
teamYoma: UI designer with many years of experience, dedicated to the users and their needs. Always inspired and curious, visual freak and pixel perfect person.
teamKatrina: A 20-something full stack designer in the making. Has over 5 years of experience. Likes the phrase 'rebel just for kicks'. Thinks that the most powerful graphic chip is your imagination.
teamJelena: Architect turned Experience designer. Passionate about technology and daily inspired by the way it shapes our lives today. Easily amused with wild patterns and unexpected colour combos. Whitespace is her jam.
teamKatarina: Hello, my name is Katarina and I'm a graphic designer. I do really hope that the work that I do can influence other people and make them exited to try to find their passion.
officeText: Our office is located on the last three floors of an old building in the city center. We have a wonderfull view of the entire city from the rooftop terrace where we sip our coffee in the morning and chat. It’s a great place to make great things.
